FOR Vittupaa1980
In folder Simobject/Airplane/A_C panel, You mean THE GPS GAUGE...
Open any default airplane,open panel.cfg 
Search for line "GPS", copy and paste the group of line into the "panel.cfg" of A300.

If you want it to pop up, set it at the beginning of the txt, after "WINDOW TITLES". Don't forget to name it+number in that W.Titles group.
